Piezo Buzzer 

Functions provided to:
- Run Startup Melodie at Boot
- Run Shutdown Melodie when Safe Power Offer Button B Pressed
- Run GenerateForDay Tone when Button A Pressed

#Connect Buzzer to the following GPIO Pints
#PIN  13 +ve (Red)
#PIN GRN -ve (Black)

#Boot Configuration
#*****************************************
#Add startup_buzzer.py to boot files in command line:
sudo nano /etc/rc.local   # Create Boot File 
sudo chmod +x /etc/rc.local # Make Boot File Executable
sudo reboot # Reboot System
